'''Tamsirwa n wakal''' d yiwen n yirem yettusemrasen i wakken ad immel aswir n ufaris [[Imɣi|amɣaw]]  i izmer [[akal (tasnakalt)|wakal]] ad t-id-yefk s ddaw n kra n tewtilin. Dɣa beṭṭu n temsirwa n wakal yettili-d ɣef 3 n yiswiren ifizikanen, [[takrura|ikruranen]] d [[tasnudert|yisnudranen]] 
== Iswiren n temsirwa n wakal ==
* '''Tamsirwa tafizikant''': tugel ɣer usalel d temsukt n wakal, yakk d telqi-ines d tɣara n tnegwa timɣuzanin ɣef wacu tebna.
* '''Tamsirwa takrurant''': agbar n wakal ɣef yiferdisen imeččiyen usfiken i gemmu n yimɣan.
* '''Tamsirwa tasnudrant''': d azal n wermud n [[amuddir|yimuddiren]] n wakal d yiɣersiwen-is, armud-a isguccul-d atig n tuɣalin n yimɣuzen seg telɣiwin-nsen tigmanin ɣer telɣiwin anda yezmer yimɣi ad ten-isumm.
